             was indicted for <rs id="t18270913-141-off807" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18270913-141-off807" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-141-off807" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18270913-141-cd808" type="crimeDate">15th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18270913-141-off807 t18270913-141-cd808"></join>, 1 piece of gold, of the value of 10s.; 1 sovereign, and 3 pieces of foreign silver coin, value 4s. 6d.
            </rs>, the property of 
               
                  <persName id="t18270913-141-victim1434" type="victimName">
                     Michael 
                     Moore
                  <interp inst="t18270913-141-victim1434" type="surname" value="Moore"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18270913-141-victim1434" type="given" value="Michael"></interp>
